{"tid":246391,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟比比鳥有冇唱個句 傳承着過去叫世間驚訝","createTime":"2017-05-17T03:29:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-17T04:18:10.000Z","uid":84840,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"99b028aeb2541b16b4f9794c2d830b01ad043a32","tid":246391,"uid":84840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:29:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/af5gsU-5NAw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Faf5gsU-5NAw&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=e4808c67\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/af5gsU-5NAw</a><br />\n比比鳥唱歌好聽就眾所鳩知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n特別係櫻花樹下個時既震音，同各種既禮讓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾軒jai唱d高音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今日突然見到呢條片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係0:46既時候，比比鳥口型唱出：<br />\n傳承着過去叫世間驚訝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個種深情，個假音，同埋最後唱左出黎之後既微微一笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇得出佢好自信好滿意自己唱得咁好聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦睇得出比比鳥既歌喉又進步左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n鳩柏豪，加油！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"212eb696ffd28f5498e7d3199643beac714268cf","tid":246391,"uid":84840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1932a8a5ace97bcaabc833b46f114f2948fc8716","tid":246391,"uid":84840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-17T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8029849dabe7797671e9ddbf8e7105072a1a9cda","tid":246391,"uid":84840,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cite